'''Michel Bessis''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (1) 2007 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[Buffett Cup]] (1) 2008 

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
